AGENT: REFACTOR
FEATURE: phase4_accessibility
DATE: 2026-03-17
STATUS: DONE
SUMMARY: 3 bugs fixed, 1 shared utility created, 7 test files deduplicated; 12 files modified + 1 created

ISSUES_FIXED:
  BUG-01 (CRITICAL): TicketStatusBadge and TicketTypeBadge silently dropped aria-hidden prop —
    both components now accept 'aria-hidden'?: boolean and forward it to the <span> DOM element.
    Without this fix, RST-02 intent was unmet: badges inside RecentTicketsTable links were still
    read by screen readers despite the parent Link having aria-label.

  BUG-02 (DEAD CODE): src/lib/a11y/focus-utils.ts was never imported anywhere.
    FeedbackForm.tsx replaced its inline useEffect focus pattern with useFocusOnMount() from
    the shared utility, giving focus-utils.ts its first consumer.
    Also removed the now-unused `useEffect` import from FeedbackForm.tsx.

  BUG-03 (DUPLICATION ×7): Identical configureAxe({...}) block repeated in all 7 React a11y
    test files (8-line config × 7 = 56 lines of duplication).
    Extracted to src/__tests__/a11y/axe-config.ts and all 7 files now import a11yAxeConfig.
    Also cleaned up a duplicate `import type { ... } from '@/types'` in admin-tickets test.

